contentrichtext.text: '''Deja Voodoo''' may refer to: * [[Déjà Voodoo (album)|''Déjà Voodoo'' (album)]], an album by Gov't Mule * [[Deja Voodoo (Canadian band)]], a Canadian garage band of the 1980s * [[Deja Voodoo (New Zealand band)]], a New Zealand band * [[Deja Voodoo (Dead Zone)|"Deja Voodoo" (''Dead Zone'')]], an episode of the TV series ''The Dead Zone'' * ''Deja Voodoo'', an album by [[Gem Archer#Heavy Stereo|Heavy Stereo]] * ''De-jah Voodoo'', an album by [[Dread Zeppelin]] * "Déjà Voodoo", a song by Kenny Wayne Shepherd from ''[[Ledbetter Heights]]'' ==See also== * [[Déjà vu]] * [[Déjà vu (disambiguation)]] {{disambig}}
